to create an environment -- python -m venv .venv(nameof environment)
to activate the environment -- .venv\scripts\activate
to chenk an modules in environment -->pip list

sometime to get the error (
    --> Set-ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned -Scope CurrentUser
    --> Get-ExecutionPolicy  
    --> Get-ExecutionPolicy -list
)

pip upgrade --> pyhton -m pip install --upgrade pip

to install django --> python -m pip install django

to create a project --> django-admin startproject project_name .

to create APP --> python manage.py startapp app_name

static file --> to manage css , js, image file django 

python manage.py createsuperuser --> to create admin userid and password  (  user - Sri , Pwd - Sri@25)